data.description: Beautiful home in private gated community of Beauvoir. This one owner home has been well cared for and is ready to move in. This cottage has a beautiful front porch and side screened in porch. As you enter the home there is a nice open large foyer that opens to a formal dining room. The large kitchen and great room are wonderful open floor plan, great for entertaining. There is a fireplace, a nice large panty and granite island breakfast bar. The kitchen has a gas stove top and double ovens, with dishwasher, disposal and nice large refrigerator. There is a half bath off the kitchen and also the laundry room is on the back side of the house. The master is separated from the other two bedrooms. The master bedroom is a nice size  and there is  a large master bath with double split vanity, garden tub and separate shower. The other two bedrooms share a bathroom. This 3/2/1 floor plan also has a nice large garage with another separate outdoor patio.
